Joseph P. Brennan III won the 2020 election but was not sworn in. SMD 4B05 is vacant as of Feb. 24, 2021.

The 2020 election in 7B03 ended in a tie between two write-in candidates: Lindsey Botts and Walter Leroy Peacock III. The tie was broken by a drawing of names from a pot by DCBOE, and Lindsey Botts won the drawing.
